# ============================================================================
# DO NOT PUSH THE UNPUBLISHED PAPER TO A PUBLIC REPO
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Until the paper is accepted and the camera-ready version is published in
# the Springer LNNS proceedings, the LaTeX source, the bibliography, and the
# figures must stay local. Posting them publicly before peer review can:
#   - Trip Turnitin/iThenticate against your own submission
#   - Surface in reviewer searches and complicate informal anonymity
#   - Run afoul of some publishers' prior-publication policies
#
# AFTER acceptance + camera-ready, you can lift this block to make the
# artifact fully reproducible from source.
# ============================================================================
